flowRoot.flowPara: The CentOS Web should accept expansion by means of extensions. An example of that is the extension "did_you_know_that". This common feauture is useful to display tips. The information is stored iside the CentOS Web database, in its own table (i.e. ext_Did_you_know). It is managed from CentOS Web Extension's Administration Panel. The design looks like this.
